    <h2>Expression & Role in the Body</h2>
    <div class="two-col">
      <img src="assets/macrophages.jpg" alt="Human outline with spleen/lymph nodes/microglia highlighted">
      <div>
        <p><strong>Where it’s found:</strong> AIF1 is expressed in activated macrophages, microglia, spleen, and lymph nodes.</p>
        <p><strong>Developmental stage:</strong> Low in resting macrophages, high during activation and transplant rejection.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
